    </string>
    <string id="ui_mcm_bwaisFireModeCheck_userMode_desc">
        <text>%c[d_green][DEFAULT] Basic: Firing mode switch buttons behavior is unchanged. New mode is displayed after switching.

 
%c[d_green][DEFAULT] Dual key: "Previous Firing Mode" key displays the current mode without switching. "Next Firing Mode" key cycles between firing modes.

 
%c[d_green][DEFAULT] Single key: Both hotkeys work in the same way: Single tap for displaying current mode, double tap for switching modes.</text>
    </string>
